<div id="review_2408294396" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2408294396" />
    <a title="Paul Gaya Ochieng Simeon Juma" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/19439030-paul-gaya-ochieng-simeon-juma"><img alt="Paul Gaya Ochieng Simeon Juma" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1453048287p2/19439030.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2408294396?book_show_action=true">Jun 07, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Paul Gaya Ochieng Simeon Juma" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Paul Gaya Ochieng Simeon Juma" href="/user/show/19439030-paul-gaya-ochieng-simeon-juma">Paul Gaya Ochieng Simeon Juma</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/19439030-paul-gaya-ochieng-simeon-juma?shelf=war">war</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2408294396" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6782041550258496246">War is an absolute disrupter. It was a rotten time to be born and grow up. Since 1939, people around the globe had lived expecting war at any time. When it came, families were separated. Friends parted and lovers went away from each other. It was difficult to correspond with one another. Indeed, in wartime most of the events will impede communication. All they could do is pray that they do not die quickly. To survive, one has to forget the past and act. <br/><br/>The Germans. They had occupied Poland and </span>
  <span id="freeText6782041550258496246" style="display:none">War is an absolute disrupter. It was a rotten time to be born and grow up. Since 1939, people around the globe had lived expecting war at any time. When it came, families were separated. Friends parted and lovers went away from each other. It was difficult to correspond with one another. Indeed, in wartime most of the events will impede communication. All they could do is pray that they do not die quickly. To survive, one has to forget the past and act. <br /><br />The Germans. They had occupied Poland and were imprisoning Jews, Gypsies, the Catholic left, communists, socialists, homosexuals, and resistants. In Italy. There was heavy fighting not only in towns but in houses too. On the other hand, the Japanese. They had invaded the British New Guinea. They usually attacked at night. <br /><br />Europe. It was occupied by the Nazis from sea to sea. China was occupied by the Japanese. They were in control of Shanghai. Soviet Union. It had been invaded by Hitler. Americans. War came unexpectedly. They were totally unprepared for Hitler and his allies. The draftees ranged from fathers to kids. Amidst the Depression, Roosevelt had to consider going to war. At the same time, fight for a higher standard of living. Fight his way out of depression. Then, the Japanese attacked the American Naval base at Pearl Harbor. <br /><br />The world was cut into bleeding pieces. People started enlisting. Among them were women. They entered the arena without fear and chose to work alongside the distrustful men who were terrified of what was happening. They believed not only that to do good one had to fight evil. The war had changed them and they had to act. Here is where we meet the brave characters created by Marge Piercy. They include, Bernice, Jacqueline, Arby, Louise, Ruthie, Daniela and others. They were fighting for love, future, and peace.</span>
  <a data-text-id="6782041550258496246" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


